Author: blackinkredhair
Text: Hey bro/sis, I don’t have advice but I feel you so much rn. Please remember you’re not alone in this, recovery isn’t a linear thing - it’s more of a messy, tangled bit of spaghetti. We can get through it, though. Sending good vibes your way, it’s rich coming from me but if you start to relapse further it might be wise to take the leap and see a doctor even if that stupid ED voice is screaming at you not to. Take care <3
